\f4\b \cf0 About BibDesk
\f2\b0 \
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

\fs22 \cf0 \
BibDesk is intended to help keep track of papers you've read, cited, heard about, etc - especially if you intend to cite them in a (La)TeX document.\
Even more important, if you have electronic copies of these papers, BibDesk can keep them organized for you and assign meaningful names to them, as iTunes does for music files.
